"O- When I first opened this and was getting a chalky smell I was thinking that I made a bad decision picking up a whole four pack, but I am really enjoying this beer. I could not see me drinking this often, but it will make a nice treat when I am looking for something different."
"O - Overall, this was a pretty fun beer. I'd like to have this on a hot summer day, and a bit colder than I cracked this one at. Very fun IPA."
